										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Recently, we‚Äôve seen a record number of people leave the corporate workforce in favor of gig work, freelancing, or starting a small business. We&#8217;ve all thought about it!</p>
<p>That&#8217;s why we dove in to find the <strong>best small business ideas</strong> for those of you who are looking to get out of your mundane 9-5 job, or just want something new to invest your time and brain power into.</p>
<p>In this post, you&#8217;ll get 85 of the most profitable and unique small business ideas, in these categories:</p>
<ul>
